## Get unique Site ID for the 4 Children's Hospital to obtain their associated Physicians' information
SiteID <- SKA%>% filter(EXPL7 %in% c ("Children's Hospital Of The Kings Daughter","Boston Children's Hospital","All Children's Hospital","Children's Hospital Of Philadelphia")) %>% select(ID,EXPL7) %>% distinct() %>% arrange(desc(EXPL7))
#View(SiteID)
#write.csv(x = SiteID,file= "~/SK&AuniqueID.csv",row.names=F )
CH <- read.csv("SK&A Children.csv")
CH1<- CH[,c("TTL","FIRST_NAME","LAST_NAME","TTL2","DOB","T1","SCHOOL","GRADUATE","DEPTCODE","DEPT_EXPL","SPEC","SPEC_EXPL","SIZE","PATVOLN","CODE2","EXPL2","CODE7","EXPL7","MON_START","MON_END","TUE_START","TUE_END","WED_START","WED_END","THU_START","THU_END","FRI_START","FRI_END","SAT_START","SAT_END","SUN_START","SUN_END","EMRSOFTWAR","EMRPRESCRI","EMRVIEWLAB","EMRCAPTURE","EMRUSERCNT")]
CH2<- CH1[which(CH1$SPEC == "PDC"|CH1$SPEC == "CAR"),]

##BCH CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="CC8")
##CHOP CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="CC8") 
##CHKD CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="CAD")
##ACH CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="AA4")

Department Distribution

#BCH
BCHdept <- CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="SPM") %>%  group_by(DEPTCODE) %>% count() %>% set_colnames( c("Department","Count")) 
BCHdept$ratio = round(BCHdept$Count/sum(BCHdept$Count),4) 
BCHdept= BCHdept[order(BCHdept$ratio,decreasing = T),]
BCHdept$label <- scales::percent(BCHdept$ratio)
ggplot(BCHdept,aes(x= factor(1),y= Count,fill=Department)) + geom_bar(stat= "identity",width=1)+ coord_polar(theta= "y") + labs(title = "BCH Cardiology Departments") + geom_label_repel(label=BCHdept$label) + scale_fill_manual(values = c("brown1","aliceblue","gold2","darkolivegreen2","dodgerblue1","chocolate1"),name="Departments",labels= c("Attending Physicians","Fellow","Physician","Medical Director","Nurse Practitioner","Physician Assistant"))

BCmr= CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="SPM" & TTL2 == "Mr.") %>% tally()
BCmsmr = BCms/(BCms+BCmr)

CHms= CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="CC8"& TTL2 == "Ms.") %>% tally()
CHmr= CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="CC8" & TTL2 == "Mr.") %>% tally()
CHmsmr = CHms/(CHms+CHmr)

KDms= CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="CAD"& TTL2 == "Ms.") %>% tally()
KDmr= CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="CAD" & TTL2 == "Mr.") %>% tally()
KDmsmr = KDms/(KDms+KDmr)

ACms= CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="AA4"& TTL2 == "Ms.") %>% tally()
ACmr= CH2 %>% filter(CODE7=="AA4" & TTL2 == "Mr.") %>% tally()

CHgrad <- CH2[which(CH2$GRADUATE != "NA"),]
YTD <- function(grad, ytd.day = today(), units = "years", floor = TRUE) {
    calc.ytd = interval(grad, ytd.day) / duration(num = 1, units = units)
    if (floor) return(as.integer(floor(calc.ytd)))
    return(calc.ytd)
}

CHgrad$YTD <- YTD(ymd(CHgrad$GRADUATE))

# BCH
BCgrad<- CHgrad %>% filter(CODE7=="SPM") %>% select(YTD)
BCmeanytd<- sum(BCgrad)/tally(BCgrad)

# CHOP
##CPgrad<- CHgrad %>% filter(CODE7=="CC8") %>% select(YTD)
##CPmeanytd<- sum(CPgrad)/tally(CPgrad)

# AC
ACgrad<- CHgrad %>% filter(CODE7=="AA4") %>% select(YTD)
ACmeanytd<- sum(ACgrad)/tally(ACgrad)
